title: DVD Shrink v3.2.0.15 -LegalTorrents
description:
DVD Shrink is software to backup DVD discs. You can use this software in conjunction with DVD burning software of your choice, to make a backup copy of any DVD video disc.

DVD Shrink will also burn your backup DVD, if you have installed separate burning software. The output from DVD Shrink can be saved as files on your hard drive, which you can then burn with software of your choice.
